{"tid":1860241,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"世衛秘書長再籲各國政府：無須為防疫 限制旅遊和貿易","createTime":"2020-02-03T14:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T14:22:29.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d4e487efb72d29baf6101834eaeee35899de9e05","tid":1860241,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞3日再度呼籲各國，沒有必要為了遏制武漢肺炎疫情傳播，採取限制國際旅遊與貿易的措施。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞說：「我們呼籲所有國家執行有證據為根據且一致的決策，全球連結性是此次疫情的弱點，但也是我們最大的優勢。」<br />\n<br />\nWHO雖在上月底宣布武漢肺炎構成「國際關注公共衛生緊急事件」，但呼籲各國不要限制對中國的旅行或貿易。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4319182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4319182&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=c4926410\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4319182</a>"},{"pid":"49ce2d42e7644b349e215eda8a7ed365aea14904","tid":1860241,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:10:58.000Z","msg":"北京外交部新發言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce2a6ec8b1e071f1a17edd94eea8bd8c30c4ef2","tid":1860241,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"當日投票比班非洲力架投贏左英國個白人專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f8549351251b0d6de27e3c20ca46f1f29df9fa","tid":1860241,"uid":263197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:12:27.000Z","msg":"屌你，做埋世貿個份"},{"pid":"ceb64c1f44e2c40050f0f8be38c7721aafb0a997","tid":1860241,"uid":302917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"如果埃塞俄比亞不幸爆發武肺嘅話，阿秘書長會唔會屋都畀人拆撚埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3a1b78a472da081076f681e4483a677db77256","tid":1860241,"uid":75072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"唔使限制 因為呢隻病毒只係會攻擊支那人<img src=\"/assets/fa